3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with a dynamical system, which can be analyzed using systems and control theory. 
4. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) - The paper deals with a model where each node updates its weight based on the weights of its neighbors, which can be seen as a multi-agent system.
